1. *Pojavio* se u kancelariji u osam sati. (He appeared in the office at eight o'clock.) 
2. *Pojavljivanje* muškaraca na koncertu bilo je neočekivano. (The appearance of men at the concert was unexpected.) 
3. Dete se *pojavilo* tokom predstave. (The child appeared during the performance.) 
4. *Pojavljivanju* se nadam da će doći do promena. (I hope that the emergence will lead to changes.) 
5. Životinje su se *pojavile* u vrtu. (The animals appeared in the garden.)